quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  110,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  110,1,jab Allah ki madad aa jaye aur fatah naseeb ho jaye
  110,2,aur ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum dekh lau ke log fouj Dur fouj Allah ke deen mein daakhil ho rahay hain
  110,3,"to apne Rab ki hamd ke sath uss ki tasbeeh karo, aur uss se mughfirat ki dua mango, be shak woh bara tauba qubool karne wala hai"
